{"tid":665693,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那人遇倫敦金騙徒成副身家無晒 危站天台準備以死控訴香港人","createTime":"2018-05-15T07:42:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-15T10:21:05.000Z","uid":39539,"like":62,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"8a4112c9218183aa8ff123e163a9f19826a62b23","tid":665693,"uid":39539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T07:42:40.000Z","msg":"一行14名內地男女，早前在網上平台購買倫敦金，懷疑受騙，苦主今晨9時許，根據有關公司的查冊，走到公司東主位於九龍城衙前圍道51號陶源的寓所，在大廈外拉起橫額抗議追討賠償，他們表示從網上獲知受騙的苦主多達3000至1萬名，涉款約900萬元。<br />\n至中午12時，其中10名苦主突衝入大廈內，直奔天台危站，保安員報警求助指有人在危險位置，警員及消防員趕到現場，警隊談判專家亦奉召到場游說，至中午1時，部份苦主返回安全位置，但仍有3至4人在天台與談判人員「拉鋸」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/15/154233_7b4f379e95228ca1af4b0765776b5f06.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F15%2F154233_7b4f379e95228ca1af4b0765776b5f06.png&h=a5fd3eae&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/15/154234_f2038402d408175d629777d25b3bc138.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F15%2F154234_f2038402d408175d629777d25b3bc138.png&h=8fa2cc57&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/15/154236_80ae65ac722f391e6cd61b7b621c1a83.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F15%2F154236_80ae65ac722f391e6cd61b7b621c1a83.png&h=4c8892bb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bceb70fcdb176094bc38903ed114629f57bea11b","tid":665693,"uid":38671,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T07:44:18.000Z","msg":"狗咬狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbe0b8c20cf07703f22399d2fb5097141a2da672","tid":665693,"uid":83328,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T07:46:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/OafDj.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FOafDj.gif&